    "updated_at": "2015-07-15T20:19:24Z",
    "body": "They are two ways of running apps:\n- One is bundling your app inside Electron and Electron will always use your app when running.\n- Another is to execute a clean Electron in command line and it will run the app specified as parameter.\n\nThe second way is implemented in default_app, if you bundle your app inside Electron you will lose this ability, but you can always reimplement in your app.\n"
