    "body": "The whole \"inside electron\" thing is far from clear in the docs - I'm\nguessing you mean 'inside electron' to be\n\nelectronbasedir/\n  resources/\n    app/ (or app.asar)\n\nWheras to run it as a command-line parameter (e.g. \"electron myappname\")\nyou'd make it\n\nelectronbasedir/\n  myappname/ (or myappname.asar)\n\nThat's not really explained in the docs at-all at this point??\n\nAlso - it opens-up a can of worms with the way OSX apps are bundled??\n\nOn 15 July 2015 at 21:19, Cheng Zhao notifications@github.com wrote:\n\n> Closed #2199 https://github.com/atom/electron/issues/2199.\n> \n> â€”\n> Reply to this email directly or view it on GitHub\n> https://github.com/atom/electron/issues/2199#event-356866392.\n"
